           <section class="block block-views" id="block-views-news-block-2">
            <h2 class="block-title">
             Department News
            </h2>
            <div class="view view-news view-id-news view-display-id-block_2 news view-dom-id-44cfd75cfb81df00009acd10134523b0">
             <div class="view-content">
              <div class="views-row views-row-1 views-row-odd views-row-first">
               <div class="views-field views-field-nothing">
                <span class="field-content">
                 <div class="float_right">
                 </div>
                 <a href="/news/2019-02-08/colloquium-talk-monday-february-11">
                  <h3>
                   Colloquium talk on Monday February 11
                  </h3>
                 </a>
                 <span class="date-display-single">
                  February 8, 2019
                 </span>
                 <p>
                  Professor Hyungchun Lee, from  Ajou University, South Korea, will give a colloquium talk on Monday, February 11, at 11:00 am,  in the Conference room. The title of his talk is "
                  <a href="https://clas-math.uncc.edu/colloquium/blog/2019/02/08/monday-feb-11-1100am-1200-noon-conference-room/">
                   Uncertainty quantification for partial differential equations and their optimal control problems
                  </a>
                  ".
                 </p>
                 <a href="/news/2019-02-08/colloquium-talk-monday-february-11">
                  Read full story &gt;&gt; Colloquium talk on Monday February 11
                 </a>
                 <br/>
