                 <a href="/news/2019-01-13/colloquium-talk-wednesday-january-16">
                  <h3>
                   Colloquium talk on Wednesday January 16
                  </h3>
                 </a>
                 <span class="date-display-single">
                  January 13, 2019
                 </span>
                 <p>
                  Professor Inbo Sim, from the University of Ulsan will give a colloquium talk on Wednesday January 16 at 11:00 AM, in the Conference Room. The title of his talk is "
                  <a href="https://clas-math.uncc.edu/colloquium/blog/2019/01/11/wednesday-jan-16-1100am-1200-noon-conference/">
                   Symmetry-breaking bifurcation for the one-dimensional H\'{e}non and Moore-Nehari differential equations
                  </a>
                  ".
                 </p>
